1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:45,670 --> 00:00:46,600
Qingyao?

4
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:47,750
Qingyao! Stop!

5
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:51,630
Qingyao!

6
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,320
- Your Highness.
- Qingyao.

7
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,180
Your Highness.

8
00:00:57,190 --> 00:00:58,070
Your Highness...

9
00:01:00,110 --> 00:01:01,670
Qingyao. Qingyao.

10
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:02,510
I came too late.

11
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:03,630
How are you doing?

12
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:07,960
Still alive.

13
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:10,950
I searched for you all night.

14
00:01:11,650 --> 00:01:12,590
I thought you've...

15
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:13,710
I almost didn't

16
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:14,840
get to see you again.

17
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,000
Last night was so perilous,

18
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,430
but seeing you

19
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:21,480
safe and unharmed,

20
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:22,590
I can finally breathe easy.

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,230
Last night was utter chaos.

22
00:01:25,230 --> 00:01:26,590
Those men were skilled fighters.

23
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:27,900
I had no choice but to lure them

24
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:29,300
toward the hidden imperial guards.

25
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:30,990
We coordinated from inside and outside

26
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:31,840
to subdue them.

27
00:01:33,210 --> 00:01:34,840
Luckily, Hero Shi kept you safe.

28
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:37,230
Otherwise, the outcome
would have been dire.

29
00:01:38,790 --> 00:01:39,680
Indeed.

30
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:43,310
It wasn't in vain that I risked my life
to save you yesterday.

31
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,790
Ah.

32
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:49,350
Protecting you is my rightful duty.

33
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:51,840
In any case,

34
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,200
I'm relieved to see you

35
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,240
both unharmed.

36
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:56,880
Qingyao,

37
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:58,710
earlier, I did not plan carefully.

38
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,640
Now, I have a thorough plan in place.

39
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,280
Why don't we continue south?

40
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:04,680
No need, Your Highness.

41
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,120
This experience alone

42
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,480
is already unforgettable.

43
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,030
Compared to wandering the martial world,

44
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:16,710
I prefer staying in the residence.

45
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,280
That is indeed good.

46
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:25,080
Then let's head back home.

47
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:27,360
Many thanks to you this time.

48
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,870
Our agreement is now fulfilled.

49
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:30,680
Hero Shi, you may leave at will

50
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,800
and do what you truly enjoy.

51
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,800
No, no, no.

52
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,200
I still feel

53
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:38,440
that all those fights and killings
in the martial world

54
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,700
are not really suitable for me.

55
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,080
I'd be better staying
in the Crown Prince's Residence.

56
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,470
Hero Shi, do you mean it?

57
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,470
I do, truly.

58
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:49,240
Absolutely.

59
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:51,310
Your Highness,

60
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,870
would that be alright?

61
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,680
Of course.

62
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,560
Having a master like you

63
00:02:57,660 --> 00:02:58,790
is more than I could ask for.

64
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,680
Your Highness,

65
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:02,800
let's go.

66
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,550
I'll hit you.

67
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:13,060
(Crown Prince's Residence)

68
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,800
Luckily, there was an underground river
beneath the cliff,

69
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,910
so Qingyao escaped unharmed.

70
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:20,990
And just like that,

71
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:23,410
Qingyao and I ended our journey
through the martial world.

72
00:03:23,630 --> 00:03:24,750
And returned ahead of time.

73
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,870
I truly admire your courage, Qingyao.

74
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,910
I've always wanted to go out myself,

75
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,240
but never had the chance.

76
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,960
When the chance comes,

77
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,430
you should travel more often,

78
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,870
and face the storms of the world.

79
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:47,470
Things aren't the same as before.

80
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:50,680
Now what matters most
is taking good care of your health,

81
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,960
and having a child.

82
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,280
A few days ago,

83
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:57,400
Noble Consort Xiao specially invited us
to the temple to pray for blessings.

84
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,800
It shows how much His Majesty
cares about the grandchild.

85
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:03,680
You must not take this lightly.

86
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,000
As for this matter,

87
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,400
you all should make more effort.

88
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,400
Don't count me in.

89
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:15,240
I'm not ready for it either.

90
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:24,790
We've just returned
after some trouble outside the city.

91
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,870
Let's focus on recovering first.

92
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,870
Your Highness.

93
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,070
Your Highness, you are quite partial.

94
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,750
I'm almost getting jealous.

95
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,760
Your Highness,

96
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,310
how did you deal with those men

97
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,430
who attacked us that day?

98
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:53,330
Naturally, they're imprisoned
to await sentencing.

99
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:55,270
Very well then.

100
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,250
You certainly have quite an appetite.

101
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,950
You don't seem in a hurry
to switch back at all.

102
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,760
I've been putting on airs
all this time in the Palace.

103
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:08,730
Now no one's watching over me.

104
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,040
I feel very comfortable.

105
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,270
You feel comfortable.

106
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,150
Your husband's behavior really
makes me uncomfortable.

107
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:16,800
What happened?

108
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,710
It's always about having children

109
00:05:19,710 --> 00:05:20,800
over and over again.

110
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,240
You privileged people

111
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:24,220
have nothing more to pursue
in this lifetime.

112
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,310
How dull.

113
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,600
Since it has to be done anyway,

114
00:05:33,650 --> 00:05:35,690
why don't you go through the hardship
for me first?

115
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,550
Once you've recovered after childbirth,

116
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:38,500
we'll switch back again.

117
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:42,670
Come on.

118
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:44,240
We're going to find Yuan Chen right now.

119
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,480
At once. Now. Move!

120
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,560
I'm not finished eating yet.

121
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,790
Do not eat!

122
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:59,740
(Moyu Pavilion)

123
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,310
Who is there?

124
00:06:05,310 --> 00:06:06,480
So early in the morning.

125
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,240
We meet again.

126
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,750
Shiyi?

127
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,830
Didn't you go to Jiangnan?

128
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,430
I knew you couldn't leave her behind.

129
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,400
Quiet!

130
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:22,920
We've switched back again.

131
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,000
What?

132
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,510
We woke up and found ourselves this way.

133
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,040
How interesting.

134
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:33,040
You two are going to extremes
for each other,

135
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,750
almost like a tragic love pact.

136
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:37,040
I'd say you might as well
be bound together for life.

137
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,320
Cut the crap!

138
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:40,600
Just tell me if there's any way.

139
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,720
A way? Of course there is.

140
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,600
But...

141
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:59,750
It is said that a celestial stone
fell beyond the frontier,

142
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,870
imbued with the power of thunder.

143
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,870
A celestial stone?

144
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:05,710
Mm.

145
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,880
What's it good for?

146
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:08,310
Think about it.

147
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,820
You two don't dare switch back,

148
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,530
because you fear being struck
by lightning.

149
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,870
But with that stone in hand,

150
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,950
you could control the strength
of the thunder.

151
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,360
By then,

152
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:20,000
maybe just taking a bath
would switch you back.

153
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,480
Who wants to bathe with him?

154
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,680
It's just a figure of speech.

155
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,710
Are you serious?

156
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,600
Absolutely true.

157
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:29,210
Once I find that stone,

158
00:07:29,210 --> 00:07:30,690
you'll surely be able to switch back.

159
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:32,000
You're not lying to me?

160
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,200
Even if I had a hundred times
the courage,

161
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,950
I wouldn't dare deceive you, lady.

162
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:42,730
Alright.

163
00:07:42,730 --> 00:07:44,600
Then I'll leave this to you.

164
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,560
You can count on me.

165
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:51,810
They're all fresh.

166
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,800
Well, say something.

167
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,680
What do we do now?

168
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,320
There's no way.

169
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,960
Either we throw ourselves into the lake,

170
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,160
or we wait for Yuan Chen

171
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,120
to find that stone.

172
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,430
How long will it take

173
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:07,990
for him to find that stone?

174
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,480
A month? A year?

175
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,830
Rest assured.

176
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,270
Even if I have to wait ten years,

177
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,870
I will never bear a child

178
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,240
for your Crown Prince.

179
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,630
You wish.

180
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,360
But honestly speaking,

181
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,800
if that day truly comes,

182
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,870
I can't even imagine the scene.

183
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,800
Watch out!

184
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,570
(Let bygones be bygones,
and past mistakes be forgiven.)

185
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:53,960
(Come to Wind and Rain Pavilion
to discuss urgent matters at Shen hour.)

186
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,040
Oh no.

187
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:59,290
A letter from the Wind and Rain Pavilion.

188
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,750
That lousy Master wants to see you.

189
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,560
No.

190
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,550
It's me.

191
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,390
I'm not going.

192
00:09:07,630 --> 00:09:08,910
But it says here,

193
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,550
all past matters will be forgiven,

194
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,880
and there's a new mission for you.

195
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,750
Who knows if it's Lingyi's trick?

196
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,320
But if you don't go,

197
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,560
that Snake and that Scorpion

198
00:09:20,790 --> 00:09:21,960
will keep haunting you,

199
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,900
then what will you do?

200
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,480
If it were before, I'd have gone.

201
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,030
But if it's you,

202
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,240
I won't feel at ease.

203
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,390
What?

204
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:34,750
I said I'm not at ease.

205
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,560
It's fine.

206
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,080
It's not the first time.

207
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,320
Besides,

208
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:41,080
your current status
has always been a risk.

209
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,150
Why don't we take this opportunity

210
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,200
to see

211
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,200
how we can sever ties with the Pavilion?

212
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,240
Didn't you say

213
00:09:48,530 --> 00:09:50,080
you've always wanted a different life?

214
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,360
Aren't you afraid?

215
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,080
I am.

216
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,040
But,

217
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,670
this is still your body.

218
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,870
So it's alright.

219
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,870
Thanks. Come, have some tea.

220
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,180
I haven't had mine yet.

221
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:23,320
What a waste!

222
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,040
Let's go.

223
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,200
You pay for it.

224
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,320
You pour the tea

225
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,340
and you still make me pay?

226
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:33,000
- Excuse me.
- Coming.

227
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,840
Silver.

228
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,000
Thanks.

229
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,240
See you next time.

230
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,710
This is the place.

231
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,160
Two hours.

232
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,370
If you don't come out by then,

233
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,440
I'll barge in.

234
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,600
What if your Master

235
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,750
invites me for a drink?

236
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:52,670
He's not that generous.

237
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,360
I think two hours

238
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,550
still feels a bit rushed.

239
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,360
What if he truly asks me to dine?

240
00:10:59,410 --> 00:11:01,170
That would be a banquet
with hidden intent.

241
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:02,720
Once the time comes,

242
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,120
if you don't come out,

243
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,960
I'll barge in myself.

244
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:06,920
Mm.

245
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,040
I'll be off.

246
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:13,990
Be careful.

247
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:15,510
Don't worry.

248
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:25,780
(Piaoyao Cloth Shop)

249
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:33,720
Please wait here.

250
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,560
Alright.

251
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:41,080
Stop playing tricks.

252
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,390
Come out now.

253
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,110
Shiyi,

254
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:50,200
you actually dared to come.

255
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,910
I conduct oneself.

256
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,790
Why wouldn't I dare?

257
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:54,990
Lead the way.

258
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,790
Master,

259
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:13,630
Shiyi has arrived.

260
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,550
Greetings, Master.

261
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,630
Shiyi,

262
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,240
do you admit your guilt?

263
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,800
Master,

264
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:25,630
I do not know what crime I've committed.

265
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,030
You know not your crime?

266
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,550
You released Bai Jun

267
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:33,480
and fought against me and Lingsan.

268
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,150
And you even betrayed the Pavilion.

269
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,360
That is a capital crime deserving death.

270
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,150
A crime punishable by death?

271
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,860
Bai Jun killed only to save lives.

272
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,090
What crime does he truly bear?

273
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,000
Even if he was guilty,

274
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:48,280
he has already been pardoned
by the Crown Prince.

275
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,910
You sided with outsiders

276
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,750
to strike against your own peers.

277
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:54,320
How will you answer that?

278
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,480
What have you and Lingsan done

279
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,000
these past few years?

280
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,960
Even without me taking action,

281
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,550
the Master wouldn't tolerate you.

282
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,160
- You!
- Enough.

283
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,840
I have already stated my stance.

284
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,320
What's past will be forgiven.

285
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:17,030
I have far more pressing matters
for him to handle.

286
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:18,750
Come over here.

287
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,200
- Yes.
- Yes.

288
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:36,470
Sit down.

289
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,560
(Father?)

290
00:14:02,370 --> 00:14:04,970
♪When a breeze passes by♪

291
00:14:05,490 --> 00:14:08,810
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

292
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:11,450
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

293
00:14:11,770 --> 00:14:14,930
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

294
00:14:15,290 --> 00:14:18,250
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

295
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:21,570
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

296
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:24,490
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

297
00:14:24,650 --> 00:14:28,290
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

298
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:30,050
♪I finally understood that truth♪

299
00:14:30,050 --> 00:14:31,530
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

300
00:14:31,730 --> 00:14:33,370
♪I lose my way in the night♪

301
00:14:33,370 --> 00:14:34,850
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

302
00:14:34,850 --> 00:14:36,530
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

303
00:14:36,530 --> 00:14:39,490
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

304
00:14:39,930 --> 00:14:42,370
♪For you and me to meet again♪

305
00:14:42,810 --> 00:14:45,650
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

306
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:48,010
♪In the pouring rain♪

307
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:52,370
♪As if you are still by my side♪
